ative of f.\"\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t]\n\t\t}\n\t},\n\t\"columns-layout\": {\n\t\tdescription: \"Renders child nodes in side-by-side columns (2 or 3). Each column is an independent sub-sequence of nodes rendered with the same node types available to the main slide. Collapses to a single column on small screens.\",\n\t\tcategory: \"typography_and_layout\",\n\t\tcontent: {\n\t\t\ttype: \"array of arrays\",\n\t\t\tdescription: \"An array where each element is itself an array of SlideNode objects representing one column. The outer array length determines the number of columns (2 or 3). Each inner array can contain any valid SlideNode objects.\",\n\t\t\timportant: \"This is the only node type where 'content' is a nested array of full SlideNode objects. The child nodes inside columns support all 30 node types recursively.\",\n\t\t\texample: [\n\t\t\t\t[\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tid: \"col1-n1\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttype: \"heading\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent: \"Left Column\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmeta: {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlevel: 3\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tid: \"col1-n2\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttype: \"text\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent: \"Content for the left column.\"\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t],\n\t\t\t\t[\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tid: \"col2-n1\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttype: \"heading\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent: \"Right Column\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmeta: {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlevel: 3\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tid: \"col2-n2\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttype: \"math\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcontent: \"E = mc^2\"\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t]\n\t\t\t]\n\t\t},\n\t\tmeta: {\n\t\t\tcolumns: {\n\t\t\t\ttype: \"number\",\n\t\t\t\toptional: true,\n\t\t\t\t\"default\": \"derived from content array length\",\n\t\t\t\tvalid_values: [\n\t\t\t\t\t2,\n\t\t\t\t\t3\n\t\t\t\t],\n\t\t\t\tdescription: \"Explicitly set the number of columns. If omitted, derived from the length of the content array.\"\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t},\n\t\tfull_example: {\n\t\t\tid: \"n24\",\n\t\t\ttype: \"columns-layout\",\n\t\t\tlabel: \"Two-column compariso